title: Skynet Rampage
description:
"Skynet: Rampage" is a tactical stealth action game set in a post-apocalyptic future.
To survive in this new world is not so easy, because you have to battle robots and other creatures of Skynet.

Robots have advanced artificial intelligence that takes into account real sights and sounds. They can think on the fly as we can, only faster.
You, in turn, will be able to use a variety of futuristic weapons and accessories, such as a laser rifle, the device creating a hologram or even invisibility.

And it depends on you that, in the end, will win using engine algorithms and brute force, coupled with your quick reaction and resourcefulness all supported by high-tech gadgets
